00:00:09.460 --> 00:00:15.563
I’ll talk before and then at the time you
can just tell me what time it is.

00:00:15.764 --> 00:00:22.542
The radio is off? You can keep it till
eight o’clock and…

00:00:42.169 --> 00:00:45.940
So happy to wait on you.

00:00:52.758 --> 00:00:58.936
Today we are celebrating a day

00:01:01.436 --> 00:01:06.678
which is a very, very important,

00:01:06.894 --> 00:01:12.588
absolutely the most important, we can say,
day,

00:01:12.789 --> 00:01:19.346
when such a great happening took
place.

00:01:20.417 --> 00:01:25.161
And it had to take place that way –

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:32.090
it was all in a way destined.

00:01:41.211 --> 00:01:45.809
In my last lectures I have told you

00:01:46.010 --> 00:01:54.734
how Christ was created first
in the heavens.

00:01:56.389 --> 00:02:05.980
In the Devi Mahatmya, if you read that,
He was created as Mahavishnu

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:16.280
and is mentioned very clearly, that first
He was created as an egg.

00:02:16.604 --> 00:02:23.784
It is written in this book, which perhaps
was written about 14,000 years back.

00:02:24.496 --> 00:02:29.059
It’s a book that predicts about Christ,

00:02:30.365 --> 00:02:35.247
and that is why people in the West,
specially,

00:02:35.448 --> 00:02:38.964
offer an egg to each other as a friend.

00:02:39.165 --> 00:02:45.256
The first existence came on this Earth
as an egg, that was Christ,

00:02:45.457 --> 00:03:00.056
and part of it was kept in that state
and the rest of it was used

00:03:01.062 --> 00:03:10.502
by the Holy Ghost, by Mahalakshmi,
to create Christ out of it.

00:03:12.440 --> 00:03:16.306
In that ancient book He was called
as Mahavishnu;

00:03:16.507 --> 00:03:19.626
means the greater form of Vishnu.

00:03:19.827 --> 00:03:22.860
But actually Vishnu is the father

00:03:23.061 --> 00:03:28.923
and He is the Son created by the Holy
Ghost.

00:03:29.124 --> 00:03:33.880
After my lecture I would like, if you have
the book, to read it out to them,

00:03:34.081 --> 00:03:39.023
the whole texts of how Christ was created.

00:03:40.062 --> 00:03:48.806
And when He was created, He cried
for His Father,

00:03:50.466 --> 00:03:54.362
as He cried also on the cross once.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:04:01.047
And He cried for years.

00:04:02.709 --> 00:04:09.187
And then Christ, in Mahavishnu state
was blessed by His Father

00:04:09.388 --> 00:04:14.407
who said that, “Your position will be
placed higher than Mine.

00:04:14.608 --> 00:04:18.420
And You will be the Adhara,” means
the ‘Support of the Universe’.

00:04:18.621 --> 00:04:24.166
See, how from Mooladhara He becomes
the Adhara.

00:04:27.495 --> 00:04:32.566
This was all done at the heavenly stage -

00:04:32.775 --> 00:04:36.531
Vaikuntha stage you can say.

00:04:37.323 --> 00:04:43.272
Then He was given birth by the Holy Ghost,

00:04:43.473 --> 00:04:48.443
who was the mother of Christ on this
Earth,

00:04:48.644 --> 00:04:54.936
who was nobody else but was the incarnation
of Mahalakshmi; means She was Radha.

00:04:55.137 --> 00:05:01.420
Ra-dha. ‘Ra’ means energy, ‘dha’ means
the one who sustains the energy.

00:05:06.107 --> 00:05:11.272
There are many aspects of Easter one
has to understand,

00:05:12.536 --> 00:05:18.920
but the most of all is why did He die and
why was He resurrected?

00:05:19.121 --> 00:05:24.189
This point I have not yet touched, perhaps,
so clearly.

00:05:24.390 --> 00:05:27.663
That’s the point I want to tell you today.

00:05:27.864 --> 00:05:32.273
It’s only you people can understand
the importance of the life of Christ.

00:05:32.474 --> 00:05:41.206
And when it is said that you have to get
your realisation through Christ,

00:05:41.407 --> 00:05:46.734
it means that He had to pierce through
the Agnya chakra.

00:05:46.972 --> 00:05:52.351
He had to be there. If He had not created

00:05:52.552 --> 00:05:58.169
this gap in the gate, we could never have
got realisation.

00:05:58.370 --> 00:06:04.956
That is why it is said that you are to pass
through

00:06:05.157 --> 00:06:14.254
the gates of heaven only with the grace
of Christ.

00:06:14.624 --> 00:06:17.482
Of course, that doesn’t mean churches,
it doesn’t mean at all churches.

00:06:17.683 --> 00:06:21.091
That you understand as sahaja yogis that
you have to pass through the Agnya chakra.

00:06:21.292 --> 00:06:26.340
Ultimately that’s the most difficult point
where human beings have to pass.

00:06:26.541 --> 00:06:34.326
Because, at the Agnya chakra, your ego
and superego are fully grown.

00:06:34.527 --> 00:06:38.786
At the human stage only this ego
is developed.

00:06:38.987 --> 00:06:43.368
Now how to overcome the ego was a point.

00:06:43.569 --> 00:06:50.574
And to overcome the ego, Christ had
to do this.

00:06:51.249 --> 00:06:57.837
When He was created in the beginning
as Shri Ganesha -

00:06:58.837 --> 00:07:07.396
you know the story how He was created,
that the mala,

00:07:07.597 --> 00:07:18.008
is the - from the body of Parvati, the Holy
Ghost, was taken out,

00:07:18.209 --> 00:07:24.816
because before Her marriage, She was -

00:07:25.017 --> 00:07:32.521
She had to cover Herself for Her bath
with many scented things.

00:07:32.722 --> 00:07:37.726
And it was taken out, all these things,
and Her vibrations came out.

00:07:37.927 --> 00:07:41.748
And She created this child just to protect
Her chastity;

00:07:41.949 --> 00:07:47.664
outside Her bathroom She put him. And
you know the whole story about it.

00:07:47.865 --> 00:07:53.725
Now there was a part of the element
of the earth in that child.

00:07:53.926 --> 00:07:57.595
Pruthvi-tattwa, was there.

00:07:57.796 --> 00:08:09.458
All other centres - all other centres have
got some elements in them.

00:08:09.659 --> 00:08:15.291
Some elements like pruthvi-tattwa is there,
earth element;

00:08:15.492 --> 00:08:20.335
then you have got water element, then
you have got air element,

00:08:20.536 --> 00:08:29.696
and when you come to this it is the light
element, it’s the light.

00:08:30.640 --> 00:08:36.051
And at this point, at Agnya chakra,

00:08:36.357 --> 00:08:42.160
He had to cross the last element, that
was the light element.

00:08:42.361 --> 00:08:46.424
That means He had to come out into
the true form

00:08:46.625 --> 00:08:55.204
of only the Divine Power, the Omkara,
the vibrations you can call it;

00:08:55.405 --> 00:09:03.237
or the absolute -

00:09:03.438 --> 00:09:08.227
you call it logos or something like that?
The first sound, Brahma.

00:09:08.428 --> 00:09:11.739
So He had to become the principle
of Brahma.

00:09:11.940 --> 00:09:13.662
To become the principle of Brahma,

00:09:13.863 --> 00:09:18.706
He had to get rid of all other elements
within Him.

00:09:18.907 --> 00:09:25.124
So the last was also the light element,
which He had to cross through.

00:09:25.325 --> 00:09:30.359
So He had earth element in Him, as He
was of the mala,

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:35.534
and all other elements within Him.
But when it comes to the Agnya,

00:09:35.735 --> 00:09:39.392
He had to give up all the elements,
that He had to die

00:09:39.593 --> 00:09:42.375
the death of all these elements that were
within Him,

00:09:42.576 --> 00:09:47.819
to become complete, absolutely pure
Spirit.

00:09:50.391 --> 00:09:56.081
What He did on subtle form works out
on the gross form,

00:09:57.174 --> 00:10:04.850
and to do that He had to die. And
whatever died in Him,

00:10:05.051 --> 00:10:08.221
was that little element of earth element
and other elements,

00:10:08.422 --> 00:10:13.063
and what came out of Him was pure Spirit.

00:10:13.264 --> 00:10:16.123
[To somebody: “Just move forward.”]

00:10:16.324 --> 00:10:21.265
Was pure Spirit that was resurrected;
the pure Spirit,

00:10:21.466 --> 00:10:28.543
the pure Brahma-Tattwa which had formed
the body of Christ,

00:10:28.744 --> 00:10:32.922
which was the body of Christ.

00:10:35.705 --> 00:10:39.738
And this happening came -

00:10:39.939 --> 00:10:47.247
Christ has done what was predicted
about Him -

00:10:47.747 --> 00:10:54.506
that He is the saviour, because He passed
through that gate

00:10:54.707 --> 00:10:59.872
to take people from this bodily existence,

00:11:00.073 --> 00:11:06.289
means the one that depends on the elements,

00:11:06.490 --> 00:11:10.094
to that existence which is Spirit.

00:11:10.295 --> 00:11:17.586
So the resurrection is where you become,
from your attention,

00:11:17.787 --> 00:11:22.393
you jump into the attention of the Spirit.

00:11:22.594 --> 00:11:29.916
When you feel your attention, when you
become the Spirit.

00:11:30.117 --> 00:11:38.322
That is the happening which has happened
to you also.

00:11:38.523 --> 00:11:45.155
But He became pure Spirit, pure Brahma
Tattwa when He was resurrected.

00:11:45.356 --> 00:11:54.729
And the resurrection is a happening
of the Divine Power

00:11:54.930 --> 00:12:04.413
which came from Mooladhara chakra as just
earth element, started growing.

00:12:04.614 --> 00:12:08.854
It took its birth from there, came up
to Agnya chakra.

00:12:09.055 --> 00:12:17.250
There Christ was created to pass through
all the elements,

00:12:17.451 --> 00:12:22.660
ultimately to enter into the Sahasrara

00:12:22.861 --> 00:12:28.321
to become a complete Brahma Tattwa.

00:12:29.280 --> 00:12:39.999
And this was a very difficult thing,
was very experimental.

00:12:40.208 --> 00:12:45.849
And the experiment was quite a dangerous
one.

00:12:47.391 --> 00:12:54.085
It could have failed also, because He had
in Him

00:12:54.317 --> 00:13:01.682
that human element, the body element
which suffered.

00:13:03.009 --> 00:13:09.118
And He suffered, because this body element
suffers, not the Spirit;

00:13:09.319 --> 00:13:13.154
Spirit does not suffer. The body element
suffers.

00:13:13.363 --> 00:13:23.532
So He had to suffer that body element
and to get over it, to get out of it.

00:13:25.339 --> 00:13:36.950
And to get out of it He had to have
a tremendous courage.

00:13:38.071 --> 00:13:43.378
It was such a difficult operation.

00:13:44.132 --> 00:13:47.706
Without Him nobody could have achieved.

00:13:47.907 --> 00:13:50.931
He knew it was predestined,

00:13:51.132 --> 00:13:58.765
but it was one of the most difficult things
to happen.

00:13:58.966 --> 00:14:05.002
I wonder how many Christians know
the significance of an egg.

00:14:05.203 --> 00:14:13.471
Now egg signifies a stage where you are
before realisation,

00:14:13.672 --> 00:14:20.987
when you are in your eggshell; that you
are Mr. X, you are Mrs. Y, all that.

00:14:21.188 --> 00:14:25.367
But when you mature fully inside,

00:14:25.568 --> 00:14:30.781
the bird is ready and that is the time
you are hatched.

00:14:30.982 --> 00:14:34.541
This is the time you get twice born.

00:14:34.742 --> 00:14:39.372
So, actually the resurrection of Christ
signifies that,

00:14:39.573 --> 00:14:45.276
and that’s why we give that egg to people
saying,

00:14:45.477 --> 00:14:52.202
“You are an egg”, a reminder of that, and
this egg can become the Spirit.

00:14:52.403 --> 00:14:56.700
And also it is written that it was an egg
when He came.

00:14:56.901 --> 00:15:03.993
First He was created as an egg. Half of it
remained as Shri Ganesha

00:15:04.194 --> 00:15:08.368
and half of it became Mahavishnu.

00:15:08.569 --> 00:15:14.429
Then He came on this earth and He departed
with all His elements

00:15:14.630 --> 00:15:19.272
and the pure vibrations formed His body,

00:15:19.473 --> 00:15:27.534
and He remained there within all of you,
to be awakened.

00:15:27.735 --> 00:15:35.591
And when the Kundalini takes your attention
through that point,

00:15:35.792 --> 00:15:40.265
there you also become the Spirit.

00:15:40.589 --> 00:15:45.372
That’s why He said that, “I’m the gate,
I’m the door.”

00:15:45.573 --> 00:15:50.309
He didn’t say, “I’m the destination.”
He said, “I’m the door,”

00:15:50.510 --> 00:15:54.069
because you cannot become Christ.

00:15:54.270 --> 00:15:57.866
That’s why he didn’t say, “I’m the
destination,” that you have to achieve Him.

00:15:58.067 --> 00:16:03.499
But He has created this space for you.

00:16:03.700 --> 00:16:11.890
You can become spiritually awakened;
you can become your Spirit.

00:16:12.099 --> 00:16:17.617
But Christ is an incarnation, He was
the Son of God.

00:16:17.818 --> 00:16:23.380
And so He is an incarnation, and that
incarnation came on this earth

00:16:23.581 --> 00:16:32.378
just to pull you out of your elements,
to make you become the Spirit.

00:16:32.604 --> 00:16:39.284
Now how is it that it was the most
difficult thing?

00:16:39.485 --> 00:16:47.085
Because human beings have created in their
heads all kinds of artificial barriers.

00:16:47.286 --> 00:16:50.760
You see, whatever we think and whatever
we do with our mind

00:16:50.961 --> 00:16:54.769
is all dead, is man-made, is artificial.

00:16:54.970 --> 00:17:00.457
Because reality is beyond your mind;
it is not in your mind.

00:17:00.658 --> 00:17:03.151
You cannot conceive it; you cannot hold it.

00:17:03.352 --> 00:17:08.704
Whatever is in your mind is not
the reality, it is beyond.

00:17:08.905 --> 00:17:14.853
So, for a human being to accept something
that is beyond mind

00:17:15.054 --> 00:17:17.328
had become so difficult at the time
of Christ,

00:17:17.529 --> 00:17:19.994
because of Romans and all these people
coming up.

00:17:20.195 --> 00:17:23.770
And we are repeating the history again.

00:17:24.119 --> 00:17:27.574
They were so ego-oriented, they were
so full of ego

00:17:27.775 --> 00:17:37.246
that to destroy their ego somebody had
to do this to create a passage.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:43.677
By His death so many things are proved,
that all those who crucified Him

00:17:43.878 --> 00:17:47.707
were stupid people, they were ego-oriented,
they were blind.

00:17:47.908 --> 00:17:51.154
They could not see what He was.

00:17:51.355 --> 00:17:56.920
They could not see what a genuine
personality He was.

00:17:57.121 --> 00:18:00.960
They crucified Him.

00:18:03.183 --> 00:18:07.847
I mean, it’s the greatest stupidity. And
they crucified Him,

00:18:08.048 --> 00:18:11.438
it was all known because these people
were so stupid

00:18:11.639 --> 00:18:15.014
that they would have only crucified Him,
what else they could do?

00:18:15.238 --> 00:18:19.691
Because they couldn’t bear, with their
little egos, somebody who is so simple,

00:18:19.892 --> 00:18:23.029
who is so genuine, who is so true.

00:18:23.230 --> 00:18:32.015
So they crucified Him and that crucifixion
came as a breakthrough for us.

00:18:32.216 --> 00:18:36.257
But message for us is the resurrection
part.

00:18:36.458 --> 00:18:41.492
Message for us is the resurrection, and
not crucifixion.

00:18:41.693 --> 00:18:45.561
Crucifixion is not the message, because
He’s done it for us.

00:18:45.762 --> 00:18:51.539
This is the point where Jews must
understand.

00:18:52.284 --> 00:18:55.842
The other day I was reading - today only -

00:18:56.043 --> 00:19:04.104
some discussion with the Archbishop
of Canterbury took place.

00:19:04.305 --> 00:19:08.752
And the fellow who was asking him was
asking him questions

00:19:08.953 --> 00:19:13.682
as if he was asking questions to God.

00:19:14.616 --> 00:19:18.780
In a way he said so also that, “I would
ask this question to God,

00:19:18.981 --> 00:19:22.401
that, why is it so many Jews were killed?”

00:19:22.602 --> 00:19:25.317
They asked for it.

00:19:25.518 --> 00:19:29.751
They wanted that they must suffer

00:19:29.952 --> 00:19:33.366
because they wouldn’t give the credit
of suffering to Christ.

00:19:33.567 --> 00:19:37.061
They thought, “We all have to suffer.”
Ego. It’s ego.

00:19:37.262 --> 00:19:42.409
“How dare anybody suffer for us? We must
suffer separately.”

00:19:43.259 --> 00:19:44.710
They couldn’t give that credit to Christ

00:19:44.910 --> 00:19:52.981
and all the later thinking was that,
“We must suffer.”

00:19:53.182 --> 00:20:01.261
So, whatever you think, comes into action
on this gross level,

00:20:01.462 --> 00:20:06.753
so Mr. Hitler was born and he made them
suffer.

00:20:10.427 --> 00:20:18.285
And the stupidity of human beings
is responsible

00:20:18.486 --> 00:20:23.481
for all the problems that are created
on this earth.

00:20:23.682 --> 00:20:26.430
The other question was, “How the children
get leukemia?”

00:20:26.631 --> 00:20:28.423
He would ask God, “How children get it?”

00:20:28.624 --> 00:20:34.330
If the parents are so frantic and speedy,
children have to get it.

00:20:35.459 --> 00:20:40.192
If you are not relaxed person when you
are married

00:20:40.393 --> 00:20:44.020
and when you are going to have a baby,
you are thinking of divorces

00:20:44.221 --> 00:20:48.271
and all sorts of nonsense, that franticness
will work on the child.

00:20:48.472 --> 00:20:51.569
Psychologically it is a left-side problem,
and the child has to be

00:20:51.770 --> 00:20:59.370
a patient of leukemia as soon as he is
born. That is what it is.

00:21:03.384 --> 00:21:10.992
So the problems are created by human beings
because of their stupidity.

00:21:11.193 --> 00:21:13.988
There is no problem that God has created
for you.

00:21:14.189 --> 00:21:17.627
He’s solved all your problems. All your
problems He solves;

00:21:17.828 --> 00:21:21.773
you have seen in Sahaj Yoga how He solves
your little, little problems even.

00:21:21.974 --> 00:21:27.750
But we create problems for ourselves
by our stupidity,

00:21:27.951 --> 00:21:38.039
by our addiction to elements, to material
things,

00:21:38.494 --> 00:21:43.466
to material habits. Matter sits on our
head.

00:21:47.272 --> 00:21:58.084
That is on the, we can say, on the level
of the earth element.

00:21:59.363 --> 00:22:04.437
Then we have other problems like
emotional attachments:

00:22:04.638 --> 00:22:07.992
“This is my daughter; this is my child;
this is my; this is mine;

00:22:08.193 --> 00:22:11.867
I’m so attached to my child.”

00:22:14.825 --> 00:22:19.349
Then, “This is my country. This is your
country.”

00:22:19.550 --> 00:22:23.330
We create problem. This Falkland camp...
Falkland this thing

00:22:23.531 --> 00:22:26.914
is an artificial problem, you can see
that.

00:22:27.115 --> 00:22:30.147
I mean, when these people went there,
these Spaniards,

00:22:30.348 --> 00:22:32.961
they all should be driven back to Spain.

00:22:33.162 --> 00:22:37.902
And all from Brazil should be driven back
to Portugal.

00:22:38.103 --> 00:22:42.510
What are they doing there if this is
the situation?

00:22:42.711 --> 00:22:46.531
But they are all human beings! What is
this territory business?

00:22:46.732 --> 00:22:50.161
So let human beings live happily wherever
they are.

00:22:50.362 --> 00:22:53.053
What are they going to get out of this
territory?

00:22:53.254 --> 00:22:57.558
God never created Argentina, Chile, England
and all that,

00:22:57.759 --> 00:23:03.461
He created one homogeneous structure,
and it is to look after each other.

00:23:03.662 --> 00:23:06.448
Like a heart is created, a liver is
created,

00:23:06.649 --> 00:23:09.689
a brain is created, a nose is created.

00:23:09.890 --> 00:23:14.758
If they start fighting - say this eye
starts fighting this eye.

00:23:14.959 --> 00:23:20.324
We laugh, but we human beings do the same
thing.

00:23:21.147 --> 00:23:23.616
We are all the time doing like this.

00:23:23.817 --> 00:23:29.885
This is the stupidity of human beings,
which is creating problem.

00:23:30.086 --> 00:23:33.071
And when you become very stupid,
somebody horrible

00:23:33.272 --> 00:23:36.176
takes advantage of that and comes
on this earth

00:23:36.377 --> 00:23:43.070
just like Hitler, and he tries to put you
right.

00:23:43.648 --> 00:23:49.993
You don’t need all that. You need only
wisdom and your realisation.

00:23:50.194 --> 00:23:54.025
And that is what is done today that you
have got realisation.

00:23:54.226 --> 00:24:00.870
So Easter for sahaj yogis all over
the world, is the most important happening,

00:24:01.071 --> 00:24:04.878
because if it had not happened it would
not have been possible

00:24:05.079 --> 00:24:08.395
to give realisation to people.

00:24:12.409 --> 00:24:14.766
I think Gavin will read it out to you
later on

00:24:14.967 --> 00:24:18.444
about what is written about Christ in Devi
Mahatmya.

00:24:18.645 --> 00:24:23.331
This book was written about 14,000 years
back by Markandeya.

00:24:23.532 --> 00:24:29.012
So imagine, 14,000 years back he knew,
being a seer, just like Blake,

00:24:29.213 --> 00:24:33.825
what was going to happen when Christ
was to come.

00:24:34.026 --> 00:24:36.638
But He was called as Mahavishnu. He was
not Vishnu,

00:24:36.839 --> 00:24:40.025
He was the son of Vishnu.

00:24:43.355 --> 00:24:51.234
And how many Christians understand about
Easter? They don’t.

00:24:51.435 --> 00:24:54.612
They - it’s - Christianity today is nothing
but a mental activity,

00:24:54.813 --> 00:24:57.255
that’s all, which is dead; nonsense it is.

00:24:57.456 --> 00:24:59.821
Just like any other nonsensical religion,
it has become

00:25:00.022 --> 00:25:04.340
another foolish, stupid religion, which has
no meaning.

00:25:04.541 --> 00:25:08.361
Unless and until you get your realisation,
unless and until you feel the vibrations,

00:25:08.562 --> 00:25:13.232
unless and until you feel this Divine
Surrounding Power, how will you understand?

00:25:13.433 --> 00:25:15.409
Because that’s the only thing that is
truth;

00:25:15.610 --> 00:25:18.380
that’s the only thing that is reality,

00:25:18.581 --> 00:25:22.972
and unless and until you achieve it, how
will you know about Christ?

00:25:23.173 --> 00:25:27.421
And fighting about Him; how can you fight?
I can’t understand really.

00:25:27.622 --> 00:25:33.152
To me, it’s stupidity gone to another
extreme.

00:25:33.691 --> 00:25:37.439
By this thing, what you do actually,
is to use

00:25:37.640 --> 00:25:42.389
all these great incarnations to kill each
other. Can you imagine?

00:25:42.590 --> 00:25:46.972
The things that came to elevate you,
to make you into higher living

00:25:47.173 --> 00:25:50.742
are now used, the same things, the names
are used

00:25:50.943 --> 00:25:53.679
to kill each other, to bring down each
other.

00:25:53.880 --> 00:25:57.204
At the most, if you reach a point where
you don’t understand,

00:25:57.405 --> 00:26:01.122
then they start saying, “It’s a mystery.”

00:26:01.323 --> 00:26:04.563
What is the mystery? In Sahaj Yoga
there’s no mystery.

00:26:04.764 --> 00:26:08.986
It’s all just there.

00:26:09.435 --> 00:26:13.672
To me, human beings are a mystery.

00:26:13.873 --> 00:26:18.704
I don’t understand them. I can’t
understand.

00:26:18.905 --> 00:26:25.427
The resurrection of Christ has to now be
collective resurrection.

00:26:25.628 --> 00:26:33.109
This is what is Maha Yoga. Has to be
the collective resurrection

00:26:33.310 --> 00:26:35.589
and for this collective resurrection,

00:26:35.790 --> 00:26:40.283
first of all sahaj yogis must decide to be
collective.

00:26:40.484 --> 00:26:47.234
Because through Kundalini awakening,
you cross, no doubt, you cross through,

00:26:47.435 --> 00:26:52.717
but you enter an area of collectivity.

00:26:52.918 --> 00:26:58.453
And if you do not allow that collectivity
to permeate into you,

00:26:58.654 --> 00:27:01.178
then you come down.

00:27:01.379 --> 00:27:07.082
Supposing you become a state beyond
the element,

00:27:07.283 --> 00:27:10.641
the state where you are a collective being;

00:27:10.842 --> 00:27:13.366
you are aware of the collective being;

00:27:13.567 --> 00:27:16.924
you are aware that you are a part and
parcel of the whole;

00:27:17.125 --> 00:27:21.654
you are aware that you have to help
your nose and your eyes

00:27:21.855 --> 00:27:24.187
because you are part and parcel
of the whole.

00:27:24.388 --> 00:27:27.112
You reach that stage where you understand
that,

00:27:27.313 --> 00:27:32.216
“I am as important as other cells are, and
other cells are to be helped by me

00:27:32.417 --> 00:27:36.613
and they have to sustain me, we are one.”
There should be complete concord.

00:27:36.814 --> 00:27:42.587
This awareness comes after realisation,
and if you do not understand

00:27:42.788 --> 00:27:47.419
that this awareness, that this collective
awareness

00:27:47.620 --> 00:27:53.417
is the only way you can stay in that area.
Otherwise you get out.

00:27:53.618 --> 00:28:03.743
You start having your smaller wells and
you just go down into them.

00:28:04.724 --> 00:28:09.481
The more you start to expand yourself,
you rise higher

00:28:09.698 --> 00:28:14.501
and then you are again with your badhas
or whatever it is.

00:28:14.702 --> 00:28:19.150
But if you think that, “I have to live
for the whole.

00:28:19.351 --> 00:28:26.181
I’m responsible for the whole. I’m
responsible for creating

00:28:26.577 --> 00:28:32.529
a nucleus of a cell which is going to look
after the whole,

00:28:32.730 --> 00:28:35.557
and if I fall down the rest also suffers.

00:28:35.758 --> 00:28:40.982
I have no business to fall down because
I have been resurrected to this point.

00:28:41.183 --> 00:28:46.751
I have entered into the state of
collectivity, where my being,

00:28:46.952 --> 00:28:50.300
which is the Spirit, is the collective
being

00:28:50.501 --> 00:28:53.543
and I have to stay there, I have to be
there;

00:28:53.744 --> 00:28:58.219
I cannot fall, it’s not the way I can
live.”

00:28:58.443 --> 00:29:03.522
But I have seen after realisation also,
people cannot get out of their shells.

00:29:03.723 --> 00:29:08.758
They still remain in the shell. They cannot
spread their wings

00:29:08.959 --> 00:29:16.531
and sing, and get out of their shell and
just fly.

00:29:16.732 --> 00:29:21.764
They cannot do it. They still stick on to
their small ways of life,

00:29:21.965 --> 00:29:24.780
in a smaller ways, in every way.

00:29:24.981 --> 00:29:29.590
In a holiday you go, you want to have
a separate holiday. Why?

00:29:29.791 --> 00:29:33.200
This is the holiday time, holy-day as they
say.

00:29:33.401 --> 00:29:38.132
Holy day. This is the holy-day. When you
are with other sahaja yogis

00:29:38.333 --> 00:29:42.827
you are really enjoying the holiday. Where
do you enjoy a holiday otherwise?

00:29:43.028 --> 00:29:48.623
Which is the other way? To be with them
is the real holiday.

00:29:49.107 --> 00:29:54.953
And that is why one should understand that
you should expand your collectivity.

00:29:55.154 --> 00:29:58.474
If you do not expand your collectivity
you are just a waste.

00:29:58.675 --> 00:30:02.931
You are a wasteful creation of sahaj yogis,

00:30:03.132 --> 00:30:06.918
which I’m sorry to say, will go down.

00:30:07.119 --> 00:30:09.189
Such people show also, in the beginning,

00:30:09.390 --> 00:30:13.691
gradually they start getting better and
better and better.

00:30:13.892 --> 00:30:16.518
And once you are there in full state,
you really enjoy each

00:30:16.719 --> 00:30:19.191
other’s company without having any fears
about them,

00:30:19.392 --> 00:30:21.629
without having any possessiveness about
them,

00:30:21.830 --> 00:30:28.446
without having any kind of expectation,
but just enjoying each other.

00:30:29.600 --> 00:30:34.546
That has to happen. Like all our cells
in our body are like that.

00:30:34.747 --> 00:30:42.381
If they can do it, why not we? Because
we have so much of sense;

00:30:42.582 --> 00:30:46.241
at least we think we have more sense
than the cells have.

00:30:46.442 --> 00:30:49.206
At least it is expected, because we have
evolved so much

00:30:49.407 --> 00:30:52.019
from a unicell to this state.

00:30:52.220 --> 00:30:56.603
And then you are the epitome of God’s
creation;

00:30:56.804 --> 00:31:00.249
you are the topmost people. Then why not?

00:31:00.450 --> 00:31:03.547
When you are resurrected, the first thing
that should happen to you

00:31:03.748 --> 00:31:07.304
is to understand that you are no more
an individual,

00:31:07.505 --> 00:31:11.634
but you are a collective being. You are
no more an individual.

00:31:11.857 --> 00:31:21.223
All things which make you circumcise
your individuality - throw that away.

00:31:21.952 --> 00:31:25.240
You are no more an individual. All problems
which come to you

00:31:25.441 --> 00:31:34.340
as individual problems are absolutely
useless, false, wasteful.

00:31:34.541 --> 00:31:39.465
Think of the collective problems. I enjoy
such people.

00:31:39.666 --> 00:31:44.964
Like the other day Fergie was anxious
to know about Bristol -

00:31:45.165 --> 00:31:50.413
which points are there, which are giving
vibrations from the Mother Earth.

00:31:50.614 --> 00:31:53.759
He’s worried about the whole of Bristol -
all the Jamaicans,

00:31:53.960 --> 00:31:59.288
then about the whole Britain - British
people,

00:31:59.489 --> 00:32:03.283
and then of the whole world you should be.
That’s what one should think.

00:32:03.484 --> 00:32:06.731
One should not think, “How will my daughter
get married?

00:32:06.932 --> 00:32:09.084
How can I get a ticket to go there?”

00:32:09.285 --> 00:32:11.656
All these nonsensical ideas should be
given up

00:32:11.857 --> 00:32:14.955
because you are now entered into
the Kingdom of God

00:32:15.156 --> 00:32:18.222
and He is going to look after you.

00:32:18.452 --> 00:32:23.170
Because that state you establish within
yourself that you are a collective being.

00:32:23.371 --> 00:32:26.927
All other things will drop out. Gradually
everybody will be molded.

00:32:27.128 --> 00:32:32.067
Even the most difficult I have seen,
have improved.

00:32:32.268 --> 00:32:35.469
But what about you, the one who is
improving everybody else,

00:32:35.670 --> 00:32:38.472
what about you? How far you are there?

00:32:38.673 --> 00:32:41.714
How far in your faith that you know that,

00:32:41.915 --> 00:32:44.995
“I have entered into the Kingdom of God

00:32:45.196 --> 00:32:49.798
and that every action mine is looked
after and guided

00:32:49.999 --> 00:32:52.556
by His power and I’m aware of it.

00:32:52.757 --> 00:32:56.587
I’m aware that I have entered into
the Kingdom of God

00:32:56.788 --> 00:32:59.624
which is expressed through my
collectivity.”

00:32:59.825 --> 00:33:04.938
So collectivity is the nature
of a sahaj yogi.

00:33:05.922 --> 00:33:09.068
And that’s what one has to realise.

00:33:09.269 --> 00:33:12.297
May God bless you all.

00:33:12.604 --> 00:33:17.477
Is it all right now? Just time.

00:33:20.885 --> 00:33:25.881
How I manage it, without looking
at the watch?

00:33:59.586 --> 00:34:02.920
Come forward. There’s some people standing.

00:34:03.121 --> 00:34:07.766
Come forward. I’ll have some water.

00:34:08.227 --> 00:34:11.191
First some tea.

00:34:31.126 --> 00:34:37.973
I mean, all these lectures if you could
tape [Hallo, Athena, hallo!] –

00:34:38.953 --> 00:34:44.086
if you could tape all these and sort of
send some of them to France and –

00:34:44.287 --> 00:34:48.356
or from Lille they have come both of them –

00:34:48.557 --> 00:34:55.283
and I think it should work out.

00:34:55.483 --> 00:34:58.770
Because first the people come in, then
they disappear.

00:34:58.971 --> 00:35:05.002
As usual, that’s the common feature,
you see. Then gradually they…

00:35:06.293 --> 00:35:09.054
Yogi: Mother?
Shri Mataji: It’s lovely.

00:35:09.255 --> 00:35:11.899
Yogi: If someone makes a list of Your
lectures,

00:35:12.100 --> 00:35:16.049
what You’ve been speaking about, as it
was along which we got one,

00:35:16.272 --> 00:35:18.679
we can print a list each month
on a newsletter,

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:21.333
so the people in other centres can write
and ask for tapes in writing,

00:35:21.534 --> 00:35:23.529
ask which wants…
Shri Mataji: That’s a good thing.

00:35:23.730 --> 00:35:28.022
You must every time I speak you will give
it a heading.

00:35:28.223 --> 00:35:32.637
All that we should. What is it?

00:35:32.838 --> 00:35:34.698
Is it coming?
Yogi: The radio programme.

00:35:34.898 --> 00:35:38.260
Shri Mataji: Ah, is it coming?

00:35:40.365 --> 00:35:43.344
It’s still time.

00:35:44.006 --> 00:35:47.572
Yes, that is important. I agree

00:35:47.773 --> 00:35:52.565
that we must have a list of things where…

00:35:52.766 --> 00:35:55.267
You have to give it a title - you see,
I have no titles,

00:35:55.468 --> 00:35:59.406
but you have to give a title. For example
what you can say

00:35:59.607 --> 00:36:07.483
is the Resurrection of Christ, or something
about Easter.

00:36:14.714 --> 00:36:18.410
Actually you can contact this Bishop
of Canterbury.

00:36:18.611 --> 00:36:27.457
This - you know... Poor man, he is not such
a staunch Christian, I feel, the way…

00:36:29.438 --> 00:36:32.353
I think next time you may write a letter
to him,

00:36:32.554 --> 00:36:35.341
and some of you can go and see him.

00:36:35.542 --> 00:36:38.617
And Gregoire comes, and three-four people
you should ask for a thing.

00:36:38.817 --> 00:36:42.828
And you should say - today’s, can you get
today’s Times?

00:36:43.029 --> 00:36:45.067
Or if you can telephone to my servant,

00:36:45.268 --> 00:36:49.432
tell him not to throw today’s newspaper,
he’s a good thrower

00:36:49.633 --> 00:36:52.328
Very good at throwing. Can somebody
telephone to him?

00:36:52.528 --> 00:36:57.673
Is a phone here available? John?

00:36:57.873 --> 00:37:01.711
Yogi: He used to be in the cathedral
of Saint-Albans. Shri Mataji: Eh?

00:37:01.911 --> 00:37:04.624
Yogi: He used to be in the cathedral
of Saint-Albans. You know?

00:37:04.825 --> 00:37:07.740
He was there when You were there.
Gavin: When You were in St. Albans,

00:37:07.941 --> 00:37:10.807
when Djamel was living at St. Alban,
You visited there,

00:37:11.007 --> 00:37:13.382
he was the bishop there. That time.
Yogi: He was the bishop there.

00:37:13.582 --> 00:37:16.695
Shri Mataji: How was he?
Yogi: I didn’t know him at that time,

00:37:16.896 --> 00:37:20.573
but soon after You visited, he got
promoted.

00:37:20.774 --> 00:37:24.776
Shri Mataji: Really? Good idea!

00:37:24.977 --> 00:37:29.659
So we can write to him. [Yogi: Yes] I might
have met him there also, possibly.

00:37:29.860 --> 00:37:35.090
Might have seen him.
[Yogi: “It’s quite possible, yes”]

00:38:06.294 --> 00:38:12.982
Gavin, you have to collect my passport
tomorrow. All right?

00:38:13.183 --> 00:38:18.695
Then I would say, on 5th of May,

00:38:18.896 --> 00:38:22.965
if you people could collect some money
for this building.

00:38:23.166 --> 00:38:27.863
That’s a good day, when you can give it
to me, or to Gregoire [Yogi: Yes],

00:38:28.064 --> 00:38:32.227
and we can put that money in the bank,
we have opened now an account for that.

00:38:32.428 --> 00:38:36.368
Any amount that people want to give,
and the first amount –

00:38:36.583 --> 00:38:40.264
and also Lille people wanted to give
some money.

00:38:40.465 --> 00:38:43.795
I told them that’s for our, you should
give it for our building account,

00:38:43.995 --> 00:38:48.322
because we have to have a building now,
it’s absolutely eminent.

00:38:48.523 --> 00:38:52.350
Before I go back, you could have money

00:38:52.551 --> 00:39:01.091
for which you can also tell Warren

00:39:01.292 --> 00:39:03.957
that this is what is decided.

00:39:04.158 --> 00:39:09.503
Then the first amount should go on the 5th,
would be a good idea.

00:39:09.704 --> 00:39:15.651
And I’ve got the account number also,
so you can send it

00:39:15.852 --> 00:39:20.377
in the name of Gregoire, and the account
number I’ll give it to you.

00:39:20.578 --> 00:39:26.562
If you want, it should be all right.

00:39:26.769 --> 00:39:31.104
Gavin: May I ask You to find out how many
people are about to go to Paris from here?

00:39:31.304 --> 00:39:35.511
Shri Mataji: Now. Now, for Paris, the thing
is, it is on Tuesday,

00:39:35.712 --> 00:39:38.991
the programme is on Tuesday.

00:39:39.905 --> 00:39:46.119
And she has arranged that we go to Lille
on Sunday.

00:39:46.320 --> 00:39:51.551
So if you come to Lille on Sunday,

00:39:51.761 --> 00:40:00.426
after the programme, if you want, you all
can go to Paris,

00:40:00.638 --> 00:40:08.126
and stay in the ashram there. Or is it
possible in Lille?

00:40:09.863 --> 00:40:13.824
Is there any place where we can take it
on rent for a night somewhere?

00:40:14.025 --> 00:40:16.442
Yogi: No problem, Mother.
Shri Mataji: What is it?

00:40:16.643 --> 00:40:19.170
Yogi: No problem.
Shri Mataji: No problem? Sure?

00:40:19.371 --> 00:40:22.358
Yogi: There’s definitely place.

00:40:22.605 --> 00:40:26.670
Shri Mataji: All right, so one night you
can stay in Lille. Will be good idea.

00:40:26.871 --> 00:40:29.947
Yogi: If there are enough people we could
also take a bus. Shri Mataji: Hm?

00:40:30.148 --> 00:40:32.340
Yogi: We could take a bus to travel.
Shri Mataji: Good.

00:40:32.541 --> 00:40:36.893
Yogi: If there are enough people, we just
have to find out how many want to get there.

00:40:37.094 --> 00:40:41.009
Shri Mataji: Now, from Lille then we go
to Paris.

00:40:41.210 --> 00:40:44.560
In Paris you have a big place to the…

00:40:44.800 --> 00:40:51.541
that will be the Monday, Tuesday,

00:40:51.750 --> 00:40:58.813
and Wednesday we have this Puja,
in the morning time perhaps,

00:41:00.108 --> 00:41:03.579
and I would like to come back if possible
on the 6th.

00:41:03.780 --> 00:41:08.943
If 5th is all right, all right, otherwise
6th you can put it.

00:41:16.840 --> 00:41:19.751
Somebody is working it out in Brussels!

00:41:19.952 --> 00:41:23.153
Did you write to that doctor? [Yogi:
“Yes, Mother…”] Good.

00:41:23.354 --> 00:41:26.762
Have you kept his address? [Yogi: Yes…]

00:41:31.271 --> 00:41:34.484
I think on Gavin I put too much pressure
also sometimes.

00:41:34.685 --> 00:41:39.560
Somebody must try to share that also.
And you should find out.

00:41:39.761 --> 00:41:44.280
It’s easy to telephone to him, I know his
number very well.

00:41:44.481 --> 00:41:47.833
But you can find out, all of you, if he
needs any help.

00:41:48.034 --> 00:41:51.328
Magda, sometimes you can telephone
to him [Magda: “Yes, Shri Mataji”],

00:41:51.529 --> 00:41:55.497
and find out if he needs any help, for
writing some letters or something,

00:41:55.698 --> 00:41:59.202
and also for typing anything –

00:41:59.403 --> 00:42:03.121
anybody who wants to help him, you see,
it’s essential,

00:42:03.321 --> 00:42:07.689
because I trouble him quite a lot.

00:42:07.890 --> 00:42:13.439
And also you have a little account for
sending letters and things,

00:42:13.640 --> 00:42:19.842
and for telephones, a little account can
be made. Everybody should -

00:42:20.043 --> 00:42:25.416
now, because we are expanding, we have
to have a proper system

00:42:25.616 --> 00:42:30.773
by which we work it out. So many letters
come to me every day,

00:42:30.974 --> 00:42:34.969
and I’m so lazy, I just can’t… I don’t
know.

00:42:35.170 --> 00:42:40.203
I think if I write now, then another will
come tomorrow, so I wait for a while.

00:42:40.404 --> 00:42:44.474
Then I - but my attention is there. If you
write to me,

00:42:44.674 --> 00:42:47.118
I’m very happy because I know what is
happening.

00:42:47.319 --> 00:42:51.405
But don’t write very long letters, you
know.

00:42:54.392 --> 00:42:57.455
I like, I enjoy them, but if they are too
long,

00:42:57.656 --> 00:43:00.383
then, you know, the main thing is left out.

00:43:00.584 --> 00:43:08.554
We have to be to the point and properly
with the protocol and all that.

00:43:08.755 --> 00:43:13.742
There’s one gentleman who writes to me
regularly from India.

00:43:13.943 --> 00:43:16.743
His name is Mr. Brahme, Mr. Brahme.

00:43:16.944 --> 00:43:24.113
And he writes only two sentences:
one is that, “Mother,

00:43:24.459 --> 00:43:29.900
please bless me that I will be a good
sahaja yogi”,

00:43:30.101 --> 00:43:34.998
“Mother, please bless the whole world
that they become sahaja yogis,

00:43:35.199 --> 00:43:37.712
and the Sahaja Yoga spreads,

00:43:37.913 --> 00:43:45.072
and your most loving son at Your Lotus
Feet, so and so.” That’s all.

00:43:48.538 --> 00:43:54.759
Every - regularly, I must have so many
letters from him, that’s all.

00:43:56.918 --> 00:43:59.875
It’s good after all: whenever you write
praise and all that it’s good.

00:44:00.076 --> 00:44:05.546
But sometimes you know, we go on writing –

00:44:05.747 --> 00:44:12.371
like one gentleman has written, “I’ve been
working for two years,

00:44:12.572 --> 00:44:19.145
I’ve done everything, I’ve done nimbu,
I’ve done this,

00:44:19.346 --> 00:44:23.453
I’ve done this, I’ve done that and I’ve not
felt the vibrations”, you see.

00:44:23.656 --> 00:44:28.610
But the list of things he gave, you see,
made me laugh really:

00:44:28.811 --> 00:44:33.378
“Oh My, you must be fed up!”

00:44:34.364 --> 00:44:38.035
And the simple thing he is doing wrong,
which people didn’t understand

00:44:38.235 --> 00:44:40.759
that is he is doing Gayatri mantra.

00:44:40.960 --> 00:44:46.345
If you do Gayatri mantra, it doesn’t
work out.

00:44:46.862 --> 00:44:51.141
I mean, this is so common, I mean, while
we are here,

00:44:51.342 --> 00:44:57.679
Gayatri mantra if people have done,
their right side is so much horrible,

00:44:57.880 --> 00:45:03.724
and it doesn’t work out at all. So you have
to neutralise it with Lord’s Prayer,

00:45:03.925 --> 00:45:06.765
and with forgiveness to others,

00:45:06.966 --> 00:45:13.727
with the right hand towards the photograph
and left hand outside.

00:45:13.928 --> 00:45:18.964
And never to say Gayatri mantra again,
you see? But that’s what it is.

00:45:19.165 --> 00:45:25.208
But these small, small things people don’t
notice when I’m treating others.

00:45:25.425 --> 00:45:29.762
And I don’t know how to talk about it,
one by one,

00:45:29.963 --> 00:45:33.123
because when it comes before me, I know
the solution.

00:45:33.324 --> 00:45:37.222
So it’s better that you people note it down
what Mother does at that time.

00:45:37.423 --> 00:45:45.943
Now this Gayatri mantra is one of the worst
curses on human beings, I think.

00:45:46.145 --> 00:45:49.471
It is so right-sided.

00:45:50.379 --> 00:45:52.756
An Indian, if he does Gayatri mantra,

00:45:52.957 --> 00:46:03.055
he becomes ten times worse that any
westerner. Think of it.

00:46:03.256 --> 00:46:06.731
Now, can you read it? Now is it started?

00:46:07.027 --> 00:46:12.095
Yogis: Somebody has to set the frequency…
The right frequency for …

00:46:18.791 --> 00:46:25.667
Shri Mataji: Why not start the radio?
Yogi: I think everything’s on.

00:46:25.883 --> 00:46:31.521
Shri Mataji: Is there no radio there?
(Yogi: “Yes, Mother.”) What’s happening?

00:46:40.424 --> 00:46:44.162
Shri Mataji: Loudly, I can’t hear.

00:46:47.352 --> 00:46:51.568
Yogi: It begins after five, Mother.

00:47:08.620 --> 00:47:12.542
Shri Mataji: Is it?

00:47:20.394 --> 00:47:23.276
More loudly.

00:48:16.612 --> 00:48:22.140
Is it yours? [Yogi: “No, Mother… it’s
a hour-long programme, Mother...”]

00:48:22.346 --> 00:48:25.623
[Yogi: “You see, we didn’t take all
of it…”] All right, all right.

00:48:31.204 --> 00:48:37.458
That’s better.

00:48:40.663 --> 00:48:46.069
You have to go through all nonsense
to listen to some sense of that.

00:48:51.270 --> 00:48:54.751
Gavin, what have you got? You read
the Bible, I think?

00:48:54.951 --> 00:48:59.602
Gavin: Yes. It’s a very appropriate psalm
we’ve discovered, Mother, very short…

00:48:59.803 --> 00:49:02.403
Shri Mataji: Must be, must be. Gavin: ...
for the ashrams. Shri Mataji: Eh?

00:49:02.604 --> 00:49:06.918
Gavin: It’s for the ashrams.
Shri Mataji: Lovely.

00:49:08.713 --> 00:49:13.007
Gavin: “Psalm 133.

00:49:13.294 --> 00:49:16.025
(1) Behold, how good and how pleasant it is

00:49:16.234 --> 00:49:20.584
for brethren to dwell together in unity!

00:49:20.785 --> 00:49:24.089
(2) It is like the precious ointment upon
the head,

00:49:24.290 --> 00:49:28.672
that ran down upon the beard, even
Aaron’s beard:

00:49:28.883 --> 00:49:32.834
that went down to the skirts of his
garments;

00:49:33.037 --> 00:49:39.874
(3) As the dew of Hermon, and as the dew
that descended upon the mountains of Zion:

00:49:40.075 --> 00:49:46.581
for there the Lord commanded the blessing,
even life for evermore”.

00:49:46.782 --> 00:49:54.032
Shri Mataji: See? Very beautiful you found
out, I must say.

00:50:01.937 --> 00:50:06.283
Now what is it? Devi Mahatmya you read
it out.

00:50:06.484 --> 00:50:11.277
[“SRIMAD DEVI BHAGAVATAM,”
BOOK 9, CHAPTER 3]

00:50:11.491 --> 00:50:17.241
Gavin: “Narayana said:– ‘O Devarshi!
The egg (born of Mula Prakriti)

00:50:17.442 --> 00:50:22.960
that was floating in the waters for a
period equal to the life period of Brahma,

00:50:23.168 --> 00:50:28.330
now in the fullness of time separated
into two parts.

00:50:28.531 --> 00:50:31.715
Within that egg there was a powerful child,

00:50:31.916 --> 00:50:38.207
lustrous like one thousand millions
of suns.” Shri Mataji: Suns. See.

00:50:38.408 --> 00:50:44.739
Gavin: “This child could not suck Mother’s
milk as it was forsaken by Her.

00:50:44.940 --> 00:50:50.403
So, being tired of hunger, the child, for
a moment, cried repeatedly”.

00:50:50.604 --> 00:50:54.240
Shri Mataji: Forsaken because He had
to grow!

00:50:54.441 --> 00:50:58.959
Gavin: “The child that will become the lord
of countless Brahmandas (universes) -”

00:50:59.160 --> 00:51:02.757
Shri Mataji: Countless Brahmandas.
Brahmandas are universes.

00:51:02.958 --> 00:51:05.792
Gavin: “…now an orphan having no father
nor mother

00:51:05.993 --> 00:51:10.271
began to look upwards from the waters.

00:51:10.506 --> 00:51:15.278
This boy came to be denominated afterwards
by the name of Maha Virat

00:51:15.479 --> 00:51:19.522
when He became gross and grosser.

00:51:19.730 --> 00:51:27.461
As there is nothing finer than radium, so
there is nothing grosser than Maha Virat.

00:51:27.799 --> 00:51:31.637
The power of this Maha Virat, one-sixteenth
of that of Shri Krishna,

00:51:31.837 --> 00:51:38.362
the Highest Self. But this boy…”
Shri Mataji: That is Yehova.

00:51:40.001 --> 00:51:43.287
Gavin: “…But this boy, (born of
the Prakruti Radha),

00:51:43.488 --> 00:51:49.084
is the Sole Stay of all this Universe”…
Shri Mataji: Sole Stay.

00:51:49.285 --> 00:51:54.153
Gavin: “… He is denominated by the name
Maha Vishnu.

00:51:54.354 --> 00:51:59.008
In his every pore countless universes
are existing.

00:51:59.209 --> 00:52:04.132
So much so that even Shri Krishna could
not count them.

00:52:04.333 --> 00:52:08.074
If it were possible to count the number
of dust particles,

00:52:08.275 --> 00:52:12.825
it is impossible to count the number
of the universes.

00:52:13.026 --> 00:52:17.536
So there are endless Brahmas, Vishnus,
and Maheshwaras.

00:52:17.737 --> 00:52:22.857
In every Brahmanda, there is Brahma,
Vishnu, and Mahesha.

00:52:23.058 --> 00:52:28.873
Each Brahmanda extends from Patala
to the Brahmaloka.

00:52:29.074 --> 00:52:32.210
The abode of Vaikuntha is higher than that

00:52:32.411 --> 00:52:38.035
(that is, it is situated outside
of Brahmanda),

00:52:38.520 --> 00:52:42.181
again the abode of Goloka is fifty koti
yojanas

00:52:42.382 --> 00:52:48.328
(that is 50 x 10 x 4 x 2 million miles)
higher than Vaikuntha.

00:52:48.592 --> 00:52:56.742
This Goloka Dhama is eternal and real
as Shri Krishna is eternal and real.

00:52:56.943 --> 00:53:02.382
This world composed of seven islands
is surrounded by the seven oceans.

00:53:02.583 --> 00:53:08.190
Forty-nine Upa Dvipas (smaller islands
adjacent to them) exist here.

00:53:08.391 --> 00:53:12.757
Besides there are countless mountains
and forests.

00:53:12.958 --> 00:53:16.523
Higher than this earth is the Brahmaloka
with seven heavens,

00:53:16.724 --> 00:53:19.844
and below this, are the seven Patalas.

00:53:20.045 --> 00:53:23.928
This is the bounding limit of Brahmanda.

00:53:24.129 --> 00:53:26.884
Just above this earth there is
the Bhurloka,

00:53:27.085 --> 00:53:31.190
above is Bhuvaloka, then Swahaloka,
then Janahloka,

00:53:31.391 --> 00:53:34.463
then Tapahloka, then Satyaloka, and
above that …”

00:53:34.664 --> 00:53:39.361
Shri Mataji: Mahaloka. Mahaloka not there?
Maha. Gavin: Brahmaloka.

00:53:39.562 --> 00:53:43.103
Shri Mataji: Bhur, Bhuvah, Swaha.
They call it Brahma.

00:53:43.304 --> 00:53:45.439
Gavin: Bhur, Bhuva, Swaha.
Shri Mataji: Swaha, Tapah.

00:53:45.640 --> 00:53:47.360
Gavin: Janah.
Shri Mataji: Janah. Tapah.

00:53:47.561 --> 00:53:51.200
Gavin: Satya and Brahmaloka.

00:53:51.401 --> 00:53:55.540
“The splendor of Brahmaloka is like that
of molten gold.

00:53:55.741 --> 00:54:01.661
But all the substances whether outside
or inside this Brahmaloka, are transient.

00:54:01.862 --> 00:54:06.541
When this Brahmanda dissolves, everything
dissolves and is destroyed.

00:54:06.742 --> 00:54:10.124
All are temporary like bubbles of water.

00:54:10.325 --> 00:54:15.264
Only Goloka and Vaikuntha are eternal.

00:54:15.479 --> 00:54:20.328
In every pore of this Maha Virat is
existing one Brahmanda.

00:54:20.547 --> 00:54:23.663
What to speak about…”. Shri Mataji: Hm.
Pore means any – every –

00:54:23.864 --> 00:54:27.477
what you call this, pore of the skin.

00:54:27.688 --> 00:54:34.189
One Brahmanda exists in Christ.
[Aside] Thank you.

00:54:34.390 --> 00:54:36.836
Gavin: “What to speak of others when
even Krishna cannot count

00:54:37.037 --> 00:54:39.764
the number of these Brahmandas.

00:54:39.972 --> 00:54:44.252
In every Brahmanda there is Brahma,
Vishnu and Mahesha.

00:54:44.453 --> 00:54:46.660
O Child Narada! In every Brahmanda,

00:54:46.861 --> 00:54:52.031
the number of the gods is three kotis
or 30 millions.

00:54:52.232 --> 00:54:55.368
Some of them are the Dikpatis (the Regents
of the quarters);

00:54:55.569 --> 00:54:58.687
some are the Dikpalas (the Rulers
of the quarters),

00:54:58.888 --> 00:55:02.104
some are asterisms, and some are planets.

00:55:02.305 --> 00:55:06.950
In the Bhurloka, there are four Varnas
(Brahmins, etc.,)

00:55:07.167 --> 00:55:10.589
and in the Patalas there are Nagas.

00:55:10.790 --> 00:55:15.659
Thus the Universe exists composed
of moveable and non-moveable things.

00:55:15.860 --> 00:55:19.248
(This is Brahmanda Vivriti).

00:55:19.449 --> 00:55:22.230
O Nârada! Now the Virat Purusha

00:55:22.446 --> 00:55:25.590
began to look up to the skies again
and again

00:55:25.791 --> 00:55:31.078
but He could not see anything within
that egg except the void.

00:55:31.279 --> 00:55:37.180
Then distressed with hunger He cried out
repeatedly and became merged in anxiety.

00:55:37.381 --> 00:55:39.994
Next moment getting back His consciousness,

00:55:40.195 --> 00:55:43.894
He began to think of Krishna, the Highest
Person

00:55:44.095 --> 00:55:48.311
and saw there at once the eternal light
of Brahma.

00:55:48.512 --> 00:55:52.460
He saw there His form as deep blue like
new rain-cloud;

00:55:52.661 --> 00:55:56.155
with two bands [Original text reads
“hands”], garment of a yellow color,

00:55:56.356 --> 00:56:00.554
sweet smile on His face, flute in His hand

00:56:00.755 --> 00:56:06.259
and He seemed to be very anxious to show
His Grace to Devotees.

00:56:06.460 --> 00:56:10.737
Looking at the Lord, His Father, the boy
became glad and smiled.

00:56:10.956 --> 00:56:16.609
The Lord, the bestower of boon, granted
Him boons appropriate for that moment.

00:56:16.813 --> 00:56:20.171
Oh child, let you possess knowledge
like me,

00:56:20.372 --> 00:56:23.277
let your hunger and thirst vanish:
let you ...”

00:56:23.478 --> 00:56:28.171
Shri Mataji: See. Hunger and thirst vanish.
He fasted for forty days.

00:56:28.372 --> 00:56:31.716
See, all the indications are there.

00:56:31.979 --> 00:56:34.610
Gavin: “…let you be the holder
of innumerable Brahmandas

00:56:34.811 --> 00:56:39.557
till the time of Pralaya (the universal
dissolution).

00:56:40.217 --> 00:56:42.671
Be without any selfishness,

00:56:42.879 --> 00:56:47.063
be fearless and the bestower of boons
to all.

00:56:47.264 --> 00:56:52.674
Let not old age, death, disease, sorrow
or any other ailings afflict thee.”

00:56:52.875 --> 00:56:57.407
Shri Mataji: This is a sign of a Brahma
Shakti.

00:56:57.611 --> 00:57:03.125
He Himself has said before that the Brahma
Shakti, or the Spirit

00:57:03.326 --> 00:57:09.656
does not die, does not get old and all
that, and He is telling him all that.

00:57:10.787 --> 00:57:15.674
Gavin: “Thus saying, He repeated thrice
on his ear the six-lettered great Mantra

00:57:15.875 --> 00:57:21.621
“Om Krishnaya Swaha” worshipped by
the Vedas with their Amgas,

00:57:21.822 --> 00:57:27.146
the Giver of desires and the destroyer
of all troubles and calamities.

00:57:27.347 --> 00:57:29.879
O Brahma’s Son! Thus giving the mantra,

00:57:30.096 --> 00:57:34.108
Shri Krishna arranged for His feeding thus.

00:57:34.309 --> 00:57:38.867
In every universe whatever offerings will
be given to Shri Krishna,

00:57:39.068 --> 00:57:43.967
one sixteenth of that will go to Narayana,
the Lord of Vaikuntha,

00:57:44.168 --> 00:57:49.670
and fifteen sixteenth is to go to this boy
the Virat. Shri Krishna…”

00:57:49.871 --> 00:57:52.681
Shri Mataji: He is Narayana also,
Shri Krishna is Narayana, you see.

00:57:52.882 --> 00:57:59.103
So one sixteenth will go to Narayana
and fifteen sixteenth to His son.

00:57:59.746 --> 00:58:03.013
Gavin: “Shri Krishna did not allot any
share for Himself.

00:58:03.213 --> 00:58:09.291
Himself transcending all the Gunas, full,
He is always satisfied with Himself.

00:58:09.513 --> 00:58:13.085
What necessity is there for any further
offerings?

00:58:13.286 --> 00:58:15.932
Whatever the people offer with devotion,

00:58:16.133 --> 00:58:20.687
the Lord of Lakshmi, the Virat eats
all these.

00:58:20.888 --> 00:58:25.723
Bhagavan Shri Krishna giving thus to
the Virat the boon and the mantra,

00:58:25.924 --> 00:58:32.122
said, “Oh child, say what more you desire.
I will give you that instantly.”

00:58:32.416 --> 00:58:36.775
The Virat boy hearing thus the words
of Shri Krishna spoke.

00:58:36.976 --> 00:58:41.417
“O, Thou Omnipresent, I have got no
desires whatsoever,

00:58:41.618 --> 00:58:46.692
save this that as long as I live, whether
for a short time or for a long time,

00:58:46.900 --> 00:58:51.189
me have pure bhakti towards Thy Lotus
Feet.”

00:58:51.390 --> 00:58:54.558
Shri Mataji: That’s why always Christ has
these fingers like this,

00:58:54.759 --> 00:59:01.088
one denoting towards Shri Krishna and
another towards Vishnu.

00:59:02.319 --> 00:59:05.998
He’s talked of His Father throughout.

00:59:08.760 --> 00:59:10.743
“For a short time or for a long time”:

00:59:10.943 --> 00:59:15.714
He lived for a short time and for a long
time.

00:59:21.468 --> 00:59:25.358
Gavin: “‘In this world he is Jivanmukta
(liberated whilst living)

00:59:25.559 --> 00:59:30.646
who is your Bhakta; and that bewildered
fool is dead while living

00:59:30.847 --> 00:59:33.559
who is devoid of any Bhakti to Thee.

00:59:33.760 --> 00:59:37.139
What needs he to perform Japam, asceticism,

00:59:37.350 --> 00:59:41.527
sacrifice, worship, holding fasts and
observances,

00:59:41.728 --> 00:59:46.120
going to sacred places of pilgrimages
and other virtuous acts

00:59:46.320 --> 00:59:49.678
if he be without any bhakti to
Shri Krishna?

00:59:49.879 --> 00:59:53.484
Vain is his life who is devoid of any
devotion to Shri Krishna,

00:59:53.685 --> 00:59:57.179
under Whose Grace he has obtained his life

00:59:57.380 --> 01:00:01.207
and Whom he does not now pay homage
and worship.

01:00:01.408 --> 01:00:07.030
He is endowed with Shakti as long as Atma
resides in his body;

01:00:07.231 --> 01:00:11.924
no sooner the Atma departs from his body
all the Shaktis accompany him.

01:00:12.125 --> 01:00:17.602
O Great One! And Thou art the Universal
Atman who transcends Prakriti,

01:00:17.803 --> 01:00:20.942
Who is All will, the Primeval Person -‘”
Shri Mataji: See?

01:00:21.143 --> 01:00:25.397
Gavin: “…and of the nature of the Highest
Light.

01:00:25.667 --> 01:00:30.039
O Child!” Thus saying, the Virat boy
remained silent.

01:00:30.240 --> 01:00:34.210
Shri Krishna then spoke in sweet words,

01:00:34.411 --> 01:00:38.985
“Oh child, let you remain as fresh as ever
like Me.

01:00:39.186 --> 01:00:45.634
You will not have any fall even if
innumerable Brahmas pass away.

01:00:45.835 --> 01:00:51.141
Let you divide yourself in parts and turn
into smaller Virats in every universe.”

01:00:51.349 --> 01:00:53.214
Shri Mataji: That’s what He did.

01:00:53.415 --> 01:00:57.507
Gavin: “Brahma will spring from Your navel
and will create the cosmos.

01:00:57.708 --> 01:01:01.328
From the forehead of that Brahma will
spring eleven Rudras

01:01:01.528 --> 01:01:04.854
for the destruction of the creation.”
Shri Mataji: See.

01:01:05.055 --> 01:01:07.702
Gavin: “But they will all be parts
of Shiva.”

01:01:07.903 --> 01:01:11.087
Shri Mataji: That is given by Shiva to Him.

01:01:11.288 --> 01:01:17.376
You see, the eleven parts are given to this
child by Shiva.

01:01:18.718 --> 01:01:22.120
Gavin: “The Rudra named Kalagni, of these
eleven Rudras,

01:01:22.321 --> 01:01:27.290
will be the destroyer of all this Vishvas
(the cosmos).

01:01:27.491 --> 01:01:31.414
Besides, from each of your sub-divisions,
the Vishnu will originate

01:01:31.615 --> 01:01:37.157
and that Bhagavan Vishnu will be
the Preserver of this Vishvu world.

01:01:37.358 --> 01:01:41.908
I say that under My favour you will always
be full of bhakti towards Me

01:01:42.157 --> 01:01:48.360
and no sooner you meditate on Me, you
will be able to see My lovely form.

01:01:48.561 --> 01:01:53.294
There is no doubt in this; and your
Mother, Who resides in My breast,

01:01:53.503 --> 01:01:56.878
will not be difficult for you to see.”

01:01:57.079 --> 01:02:00.666
Shri Mataji: Better to see. Gavin: “Let
you remain here in ease and comfort.

01:02:00.867 --> 01:02:09.164
I now go to Goloka.” Saying thus Shri
Krishna, the Lord of world, disappears.

01:02:10.109 --> 01:02:15.686
Shri Mataji: See, it’s so clear cut. Better
send it to this Archbishop of Canterbury.

01:02:15.913 --> 01:02:19.311
What does he understand about Christ?

01:02:19.514 --> 01:02:25.162
That every pore of His skin is one
Brahmanda.

01:02:26.281 --> 01:02:28.715
So He became very gross, you see,

01:02:28.916 --> 01:02:32.303
in the sense that He came down
on this earth, you see,

01:02:32.504 --> 01:02:35.734
and then He became the Spirit.

01:02:37.576 --> 01:02:41.408
That’s why it is said, His “only Son.”

01:02:49.432 --> 01:02:51.941
Yogi: Mother?

01:02:58.140 --> 01:03:01.127
Shri Mataji: What is happening?

01:03:03.398 --> 01:03:05.948
Nothing?

01:03:06.640 --> 01:03:11.606
Yogi: Mother, may I read something for You?
Shri Mataji: Yes, yes.

01:03:12.147 --> 01:03:14.872
Yogi: Paul, Paul Duncan and I have written
this. Shri Mataji: Eh?

01:03:15.073 --> 01:03:16.957
Yogi: Paul Duncan and I have written this
for You.

01:03:17.158 --> 01:03:20.294
It’s called “Resurrection Sunday.”

01:03:20.495 --> 01:03:23.260
“We wandered lost in this confused age /

01:03:23.461 --> 01:03:26.734
You came to us like rain to a scorched
plain /

01:03:26.935 --> 01:03:29.070
We made so many foolish mistakes /

01:03:29.271 --> 01:03:32.120
But You laughed and loved us even more. /

01:03:32.321 --> 01:03:36.680
We walked always seeking Messiah’s return /

01:03:36.881 --> 01:03:39.175
And then You came with open arms. /

01:03:39.376 --> 01:03:42.019
We closed our hearts and ran our love dry /

01:03:42.220 --> 01:03:45.134
And You refreshed us with cooling Grace. /

01:03:45.335 --> 01:03:47.534
Mother, O Mother, River of Love /

01:03:47.735 --> 01:03:49.621
You wash our troubles away. /

01:03:49.823 --> 01:03:52.339
Mother, O Mother, Ocean of Joy /

01:03:52.540 --> 01:03:54.866
You are opening our flowers. /

01:03:55.067 --> 01:03:58.664
We struggled hard inside our shells /

01:03:58.865 --> 01:04:02.270
You took the eggs and made the doves. /

01:04:02.471 --> 01:04:05.941
We cried for love and forgot how to be /

01:04:06.142 --> 01:04:09.239
You wiped our tears and make us see. /

01:04:09.440 --> 01:04:12.155
We needed the fulfillment of Christ’s
words /

01:04:12.380 --> 01:04:16.054
And then Mother Mary, You gave us
true second birth. /

01:04:16.257 --> 01:04:18.986
We languished in our man-made tombs /

01:04:19.213 --> 01:04:22.674
Divine Redeemer, You rolled away
the stone. /

01:04:22.875 --> 01:04:25.072
Mother, O Mother, River of Love /

01:04:25.307 --> 01:04:27.313
You wash all troubles away. /

01:04:27.514 --> 01:04:29.394
Mother, O Mother, Ocean of Joy /

01:04:29.613 --> 01:04:33.114
You open all the flowers.”

01:04:36.203 --> 01:04:39.592
Shri Mataji: So beautiful, I think.
Very beautiful.

01:04:39.793 --> 01:04:44.817
It’s like a mantra working on my
vibrations.

