last two days –

01:05:18.114 --> 01:05:25.945
one day to Norwich, and then one day
in Cambridge, then Norwich,

01:05:26.146 --> 01:05:36.033
I think 17th is Cambridge, 18th Norwich
and again Cambridge, and then Puja.

01:05:36.610 --> 01:05:40.214
Best is to keep two days in Cambridge –
first Norwich,

01:05:40.415 --> 01:05:43.593
that will be - what date did I tell you
to have Norwich?

01:05:43.794 --> 01:05:46.381
Yogi: The 18th, Jai Shri Mataji.
Shri Mataji: 18th should be Norwich,

01:05:46.582 --> 01:05:54.101
19th and 20th Cambridge, and 21st will
be the Puja. All right?

01:05:54.302 --> 01:05:58.697
Just change that much, otherwise it’s
perfectly alright.

