Shri Mataji: Ah? Now, the one point that’s
very important to be said

01:24:47.157 --> 01:24:53.074
on such interview, you see, is that you
become empowered by your own powers.

01:24:53.275 --> 01:24:58.146
You yourself know, you can feel it,
the other person, you can feel yourself

01:24:58.347 --> 01:25:03.970
and you know how to maneuver, you see,
this Kundalini of others;

01:25:04.171 --> 01:25:06.279
you can give Realisations to others;

01:25:06.480 --> 01:25:10.288
you can cure others; your power is
released.

01:25:10.489 --> 01:25:14.741
Your power of your Spirit is released
on your central nervous system.

01:25:14.949 --> 01:25:17.357
That would be really convincing; that is
not my power,

01:25:17.558 --> 01:25:20.898
it’s your own power you can feel.

01:25:21.896 --> 01:25:26.214
Yogini: Mother, it seems, through talking
of other groups,

01:25:26.415 --> 01:25:29.528
they do all say very much the same
as we do,

01:25:29.729 --> 01:25:34.756
but the only thing that we should say –
really has to be convincingly -

01:25:34.957 --> 01:25:38.210
is that we do have such powers.
Shri Mataji: That’s it.

01:25:38.411 --> 01:25:40.245
Yogini: That’s it.
Shri Mataji: Just talking is very easy.

01:25:40.445 --> 01:25:43.262
You see, if read some books, they talk.

01:25:43.463 --> 01:25:46.670
See, they read a Sahaj Yoga book, they can
say, “I have a Kundalini awakening.

01:25:46.871 --> 01:25:49.563
I can see the chakras. I can…” All right,
say!

01:25:49.764 --> 01:25:53.059
Ask them, “Can you feel our chakras?”
[Yogi: “That’s all.”]

01:25:53.260 --> 01:25:57.747
That’s all. Then what do they agree?

01:25:57.948 --> 01:26:01.959
Then what do they say; are they going
to come?

01:26:02.571 --> 01:26:04.228
Yogini: Some of them have done, yes,
Mother, we were...

01:26:04.429 --> 01:26:06.698
Shri Mataji: I think you should go and meet
them, again and again.

01:26:06.899 --> 01:26:09.950
(Yogini: “Yes, Mother.”) You see,
Amar Samati asked –

01:26:10.151 --> 01:26:14.014
he went to Santa Cruz, absolutely a new
place.

01:26:14.215 --> 01:26:16.550
And he met people and talked to them and
told them,

01:26:16.751 --> 01:26:20.608
“See, you are not feeling anything, why are
you adhering to any group, for what?

01:26:20.809 --> 01:26:24.318
For paying money? For what? Because you
have been doing it,

01:26:24.519 --> 01:26:26.762
but you are not feeling any vibrations,
nothing;

01:26:26.962 --> 01:26:30.818
you are not feeling anything, you have
no powers.” And he convinced them.

01:26:31.019 --> 01:26:33.567
And he said, “There will be at least five
to six hundred people,” and there were –

01:26:33.768 --> 01:26:37.461
more than that, for that programme.

01:26:37.662 --> 01:26:39.363
That’s what you have to go and tell them,
“What have you got?

01:26:39.564 --> 01:26:42.280
You haven’t got any powers. We have,
we can feel you.

01:26:42.481 --> 01:26:47.139
We know this is what, this is your chakra
is here, that is there.” That’s the thing.

01:26:47.340 --> 01:26:51.547
Yogini: Mother, there is a very funny
story, we went to see some Buddhists,

01:26:51.748 --> 01:26:55.566
and I asked one of them (...) what
enlightenment was.

01:26:55.767 --> 01:26:58.341
Shri Mataji: Hm. Yogini: And he gave me
a very flurry answer.

01:26:58.542 --> 01:27:03.265
And I said to him, “Do you think you will
get it in this lifetime?”

01:27:03.466 --> 01:27:06.380
And he says: “Oh I don’t know, I think it
might be possible.”

01:27:06.581 --> 01:27:09.521
And I said, “Well, how would you know it
when you get it?”

01:27:09.722 --> 01:27:12.616
He said, “Oh, I suppose it will dawn on me
one day.”

01:27:12.817 --> 01:27:14.874
And as he said that, his Kundalini came up!

01:27:15.090 --> 01:27:16.416
Shri Mataji: It will what, it will what?

01:27:16.617 --> 01:27:19.181
Yogini: He said, “I suppose it will dawn
on me one day.”

01:27:19.405 --> 01:27:22.993
And as he said it his Kundalini came up.

01:27:26.279 --> 01:27:28.730
Shri Mataji: Good.

01:27:32.190 --> 01:27:35.494
I’m also sending – you see these… Somehow,
with my husband’s job,

01:27:35.695 --> 01:27:39.242
I meet people who are seekers and who are
placed at the helm of affairs.

01:27:39.443 --> 01:27:41.018
