Shri Mataji: He tried to awaken their
Kundalini.

02:15:59.663 --> 02:16:03.902
It’s not written in this book; I wish they
had written.

02:16:04.103 --> 02:16:07.152
Many Christians would have been saved.

02:16:07.360 --> 02:16:11.946
All right. So better? Wash my hands.

