02:17:49.969 --> 02:17:53.081
and did cast himself into the sea.

02:17:53.282 --> 02:17:57.006
⁸And the other disciples came in a little
ship;

02:17:57.207 --> 02:18:01.037
(for they were not far from land, but as it
