He saith unto him, Feed my sheep.

02:19:27.447 --> 02:19:32.713
¹⁷He saith unto him the third time, Simon,
son of Jonas, lovest thou me?

02:19:32.932 --> 02:19:37.537
Peter was grieved because he said unto him
the third time, Lovest thou me?

02:19:37.738 --> 02:19:40.949
And he said unto him, Lord, thou knowest
all these things;

02:19:41.149 --> 02:19:48.218
thou knowest that I love thee. Jesus saith
unto him, Feed my sheep.

