02:21:18.635 --> 02:21:21.934
could not contain the books that shall
(should) be written.

02:21:22.159 --> 02:21:24.288
Shri Mataji: Ah, you see, He said that,
“Thou shalt not die.”

02:21:24.489 --> 02:21:29.055
What does that mean? Nobody dies, isn’t it?

02:21:29.256 --> 02:21:34.200
And that you’ll be revived, you’ll have
an Eternal Life!

02:22:23.092 --> 02:22:28.813
Good. Now …

02:22:29.014 --> 02:22:32.097
that should do.

02:22:45.049 --> 02:22:48.324
Just pour it.

02:22:50.848 --> 02:22:56.405
Yes. Is it over?

02:23:00.709 --> 02:23:06.378
You didn’t show - read the Resurrection
itself.

02:23:21.128 --> 02:23:24.873
... you should pour some honey also,
pour something.

02:23:25.074 --> 02:23:29.253
Better. Honey is there.

02:23:31.503 --> 02:23:34.392
Pour all that.

02:23:41.204 --> 02:23:44.789
It’s good. That will do.

02:23:44.990 --> 02:23:49.939
Now. More milk.

02:23:51.430 --> 02:23:54.772
More milk.

02:23:56.513 --> 02:23:59.532
Gavin? [Gavin: “Yes, Mother”]

02:24:12.468 --> 02:24:15.659
More milk.

02:24:41.593 --> 02:24:44.563
Good.

