02:26:11.146 --> 02:26:14.385
which were written in the law of Moses,
and in the prophets,

02:26:14.585 --> 02:26:18.934
and in the psalms, concerning me.

02:26:19.351 --> 02:26:26.055
⁴⁵Then opened he their understanding,
