02:26:26.255 --> 02:26:29.059
⁴⁶And said unto them, Thus it is written,

02:26:29.260 --> 02:26:31.884
and thus it behoved Christ to suffer,

02:26:32.085 --> 02:26:36.730
and to rise from the dead the third day:

