02:29:27.194 --> 02:29:29.848
Is food ready or…

02:29:30.049 --> 02:29:33.598
We can have havan and then have the food,
whichever way you see.

02:29:33.799 --> 02:29:38.512
I’m free tonight, for the whole night.

