Gavin: Mother, for this puja we don’t give
You a sari.

02:29:51.249 --> 02:29:55.197
Shri Mataji: Oh, good.
Gavin: We give You something more symbolic.

02:29:55.398 --> 02:30:00.140
Shri Mataji: That’s good. May God
bless you.

02:30:12.907 --> 02:30:18.898
Beautiful. Can I open?

02:30:32.351 --> 02:30:34.954
Beautiful.

