It’s too much, Gavin, it’s too much.

02:32:47.799 --> 02:32:50.716
Very beautiful.

02:32:52.562 --> 02:32:55.303
Thank you.

02:32:55.504 --> 02:32:58.368
Gavin and yogis: Jai Mataji.

02:33:00.363 --> 02:33:03.054
Shri Mataji: Thank you very much,
thank you.

02:33:03.255 --> 02:33:05.661
It’s so beautiful, you can’t imagine.
Very beautiful.

02:33:05.868 --> 02:33:11.857
It has that pradakshina round the Spirit.

02:33:12.058 --> 02:33:16.068
See? It’s beautiful. What a choice,
it's a beauty.

