02:34:23.047 --> 02:34:30.326
Eh? What’s this for? Now what is there?
This.

02:34:30.732 --> 02:34:36.221
Hm?  It’s flower? This is - flower?

02:34:41.818 --> 02:34:46.527
What happened? You’ve been crying!

02:34:49.907 --> 02:34:52.597
Don’t cry.

02:34:54.045 --> 02:34:58.911
Did you see this one is? What’s that?

02:34:59.240 --> 02:35:03.593
She is becoming a farmer or what?

02:35:05.278 --> 02:35:07.940
See this flower.

02:35:09.861 --> 02:35:12.250
Good?

02:35:27.189 --> 02:35:29.682
Nice.

02:35:36.885 --> 02:35:39.861
So what about chana?

02:35:44.151 --> 02:35:46.628
Now what’s that?

02:35:47.210 --> 02:35:50.338
She is getting taller!

02:35:51.795 --> 02:35:56.142
So now, what is the programme, next?
Is - what about dinner?

02:35:56.343 --> 02:36:03.134
Or should we have the puja first? Who is
the in-charge?

