and Norman should assist him,

02:36:14.508 --> 02:36:18.224
and they should form all the rules and
regulations of this place.

02:36:18.425 --> 02:36:22.832
And when Harry comes, his wife will look
after the cooking side of it,

02:36:23.033 --> 02:36:26.295
and the cleanliness of the place, because
she’ll stay at home,

02:36:26.496 --> 02:36:30.467
and Harry will look after the Puja part.

02:36:34.031 --> 02:36:36.260
I think to the other ashram also, whatever
is needed

02:36:36.461 --> 02:36:42.307
you must do the needful, make it
a comfortable place.

