Yogi: No, I think this is being sorted out
now, Mother.

02:38:50.189 --> 02:38:53.165
Shri Mataji: Hm?
Yogi: We are sorting this out now, Mother…

02:38:53.366 --> 02:38:57.163
Shri Mataji: What about the gas, gas
connection?

02:38:57.364 --> 02:39:01.681
Yogi: Gas is on, Mother. Other yogi:
