02:42:44.219 --> 02:42:47.114
Gavin (reads): “Mother, for Your birthday,
we have made a pledge:

02:42:47.393 --> 02:42:50.807
we should dedicate our life to Sahaja Yoga.

02:42:51.015 --> 02:42:56.836
What is this pledge, and to what extent
can we follow this pledge?

02:42:57.037 --> 02:43:01.950
We have to be collectively surrended
to our Beloved Mother.

02:43:02.153 --> 02:43:08.538
We are collective the moment our Spirit
rejoins Your Heart, Mother.

02:43:08.739 --> 02:43:15.307
We are collective the moment Your Smile
irradiates our beings.

02:43:15.508 --> 02:43:19.972
We are collective the moment Your eyes
of love and compassion

02:43:20.173 --> 02:43:25.747
pour into our heart their Divine flow
of unequalled beauty.

02:43:25.948 --> 02:43:31.538
We are collective the moment Your heart
touches with softness and peace

02:43:31.740 --> 02:43:35.694
the inner part of our Selves;

02:43:35.895 --> 02:43:40.064
collective means one heart, in the Heart
of the Divine.

02:43:40.265 --> 02:43:44.673
One smile, in the Smile of God Almighty;

02:43:44.874 --> 02:43:52.002
one joy melted in the Divine Joy of Your
Glory, You, our Beloved Mother.

02:43:52.203 --> 02:43:57.631
One sound, expressed through the extremely
beautiful melody of Your Voice;

02:43:57.832 --> 02:44:01.827
then, we surrender to You.

02:44:02.028 --> 02:44:05.363
Surrender is a happening;

02:44:05.564 --> 02:44:12.615
it is the exchange of love between
the Mother and the child.

02:44:13.228 --> 02:44:16.483
Let us melt Your Heart,

02:44:16.684 --> 02:44:21.480
let us dissolve ourselves in the inner part
of Your Heart;

02:44:21.691 --> 02:44:26.169
so that we can see and feel the glory
of Your Becoming;

02:44:26.370 --> 02:44:33.035
the tenderness of Your Face and the grace
of Your Hands.

02:44:34.298 --> 02:44:41.311
But surrender is more: surrender is action
magnified through collectivity.

02:44:41.530 --> 02:44:45.254
How can we love You, Mother, if we do
not act?

02:44:45.455 --> 02:44:49.551
How can we follow You if we don’t find?

02:44:49.752 --> 02:44:52.276
How can we be the Golden Builders,

02:44:52.477 --> 02:44:57.862
if we do not build Your love and compassion
in our hearts?

02:44:58.063 --> 02:45:02.303
Let us pray to You, Mother, to be Your
soldiers,

02:45:02.504 --> 02:45:06.402
the soldiers of truth and of righteousness.

02:45:06.603 --> 02:45:09.211
Please, take out our passivity.

02:45:09.412 --> 02:45:14.605
Kill our inaction. Destroy our apathy.

02:45:14.806 --> 02:45:18.558
Brothers and sisters, let us wake up
to gain the battlefield:

02:45:18.759 --> 02:45:22.595
are we sahaja yogis or are we cowards?

02:45:22.803 --> 02:45:27.265
Do we realise that we are the children
of Adi Shakti?

02:45:27.466 --> 02:45:31.693
Do we see, every second of our life,
that She is Almighty,

02:45:31.894 --> 02:45:38.593
that everything which lives and pulsates
comes from Her, and goes to Her?

02:45:38.794 --> 02:45:46.225
That the whole universe is in Her command,
and bows at Her Lotus Feet?

02:45:46.434 --> 02:45:51.449
That all the angels are protecting us,
to win the war?

02:45:51.650 --> 02:45:55.129
We are not allowed to sit down, we have
to stand up,

02:45:55.330 --> 02:46:00.395
to take the sword, to hold it firm in our
hands:

02:46:00.596 --> 02:46:06.750
what is more glorious and beautiful than
to fight alongside our Beloved Mother?

02:46:06.951 --> 02:46:12.007
When in the middle of the battlefield
we feel all is against us,

02:46:12.208 --> 02:46:16.999
let us just pronounce Her Name in our
heart:

02:46:17.266 --> 02:46:20.022
Your Name, Mother, like a pure river,

02:46:20.223 --> 02:46:24.089
cleans and eliminates our fears and doubts,

02:46:24.314 --> 02:46:28.706
fills us with confidence and joy, courage
and faith,

02:46:28.907 --> 02:46:32.852
because Your Name is the Name of God
Almighty;

02:46:33.053 --> 02:46:38.168
let us collectively surrender to You,
extreme beauty,

02:46:38.369 --> 02:46:43.668
extraordinary glory, eternal purity,

02:46:43.869 --> 02:46:49.443
cosmic power, greatest love,

02:46:49.651 --> 02:46:55.185
unsurpassed splendour shining all over
the universe -

02:46:55.386 --> 02:46:59.840
Mother, Mother of all the Mothers,

02:47:00.041 --> 02:47:06.152
Mother of Your devoted children, this is
our pledge;

02:47:06.353 --> 02:47:13.786
